# FastAPI Application

This is a FastAPI application that provides access to the LTB Cases database.

## Requirements

- Python

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

   ```
   git clone https://github.com/jataellen/Allard_A_Capstone.git
   ```

2. Navigate to the project directory:

   ```
   cd backend/fastapi-project
   ```


## Usage

1. Start the FastAPI server:

   ```
   uvicorn main:app --reload;
   ```

   This command will start the FastAPI application on `http://localhost:8000`.

2. Access the FastAPI application by opening a web browser and navigating to `http://localhost:8000`.

## API Documentation

- Swagger docs at http://localhost:8000/docs
- Postman Collection in file: Cases.postman_collection.json
